    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊表示，市场目前“陷入困境”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-says-markets-stuck-right-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席美国股票策略师迈克·威尔逊在接受“彭博未平仓合约”采访时表示，市场陷入了一种难以挑选股票、难以超越的环境中。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-says-markets-stuck-right-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到制裁，俄罗斯石油价格仍持续下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/russian-oil-deliveries-keep-getting-cheaper-despite-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团制裁旨在剥夺克里姆林宫的石油美元，但却未能实现其主要目标之一：提高俄罗斯石油的运输成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/russian-oil-deliveries-keep-getting-cheaper-despite-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cboe 前首席执行官 Tilly 加入价值 20 亿美元的金融科技公司 Clear Street</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/cboe-s-former-ceo-ed-tilly-joins-2-billion-fintech-clear-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥期权交易所 (Cboe) 全球市场公司 (Global Markets Inc.) 前负责人艾德·蒂利 (Ed Tilly) 将加入新兴经纪服务提供商 Clear Street，在证券行业担任新的领导职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/cboe-s-former-ceo-ed-tilly-joins-2-billion-fintech-clear-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国报告显示数千名卢旺达士兵在刚果作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/thousands-of-rwandan-troops-fight-in-east-congo-un-report-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国报告显示，数千名卢旺达士兵支持​​刚果民主共和国东部的叛乱，这场叛乱已导致数百万人流离失所，并使两国濒临战争边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/thousands-of-rwandan-troops-fight-in-east-congo-un-report-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略师表示股市上涨需要美国财报季的强劲表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/a-bumper-us-earnings-season-is-key-for-stocks-to-scale-new-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街策略师表示，美国企业需要在季度财报季中实现强劲增长，才能延续美国股市破纪录的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/a-bumper-us-earnings-season-is-key-for-stocks-to-scale-new-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织将考虑降低大额借款人罚款的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/imf-to-discuss-options-for-lowering-penalties-on-big-borrowers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一些国家担心由于利率上升导致成本变得不合理之后，国际货币基金组织将讨论对其向最大借款人收取的费用进行审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/imf-to-discuss-options-for-lowering-penalties-on-big-borrowers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡僵局风险，法国股市涨幅缩减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于立法选举产生分裂的议会且没有明显多数，投资者评估了政治僵局带来的风险，法国股市回吐了早前大部分涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市上涨，盈利预期创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周股市开盘创下历史新高，交易员们等待企业财报季的开始，同时密切关注美国总统竞选和美联储下一步行动的任何线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
